This folder contains the four following files :
1 - The Gerber files for manufacturing the 4-layer PCB (Altium Designer CAM format);
2 - A partial Digikey BOM / cart for the hand-soldering assembly step;
3 - A JLCPCB formatted BOM file to upload when placing the PCBA order;
4 - A JLCPCB formatted Pick and Place file to upload when placing the PCBA order;
